{"tid":2239110,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"強迫透視題材益智新作《超閾限空間 Superliminal》確定 11 月登陸 Steam 平台","createTime":"2020-10-11T15:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T21:01:45.000Z","uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b51accbc4259f6e0e8c46310a4bf1790a68312e","tid":2239110,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTdls2PySC0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBTdls2PySC0&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=65bab215\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTdls2PySC0</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n  由遊戲開發商 Pillow Castle Games 製作的《超閾限空間》是一款第一人稱益智遊戲，以物體在視覺上造成的遠近、大小錯覺等效果來展開一場超現實的探險。<br />\n<br />\n  《Superliminal》為一款利用視野遠近的錯覺來進行益智解謎的第一人稱視點益智解謎遊戲，在遊戲中。玩家們將在非現實的夢境世界裡進行探索冒險，並必須活用充滿景深與遠近感視覺錯覺的變化來進行超難度的關卡益智解謎；同時遊戲中還將會加入可以彷彿讓玩家們身歷其境一般，以現實為主題製作的各種物件讓玩家們拿起確認使用，也讓遊戲增添更多變化性與挑戰性，讓玩家們體驗前所未有的益智解謎樂趣！<br />\n<br />\n  《超閾限空間》自 2013 年在東京電玩展亮相後，至今已經過六年多的時間開發。官方正式公開上市宣傳影片，宣布遊戲將於 11 月 5 日登陸 Steam 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1049410/Superliminal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1049410%2FSuperliminal%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=2b13d09f\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1049410/Superliminal/</a>"},{"pid":"0aba0131d9cf68d1b5ce3feaf0dc57ca8d9e59f2","tid":2239110,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31712955ffd074999291635187b988c523d33d26","tid":2239110,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔錯wor"},{"pid":"d011701d6a349a8700b1c2ef622de3ddefdca5d9","tid":2239110,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:51:23.000Z","